></span>\n\n    <span class=\"press-logo\">Forbes</span>\n\n    <span class=\"press-logos__divider\"></span>\n\n    <span class=\"press-logo press-logo--serif\">Elle</span>\n\n    <span class=\"press-logos__divider\"></span>\n\n    <span class=\"press-logo\">BFM</span>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
