        "liquid": "{% comment %}\n\n  ============================================\n\n  CUSTOM LIQUID — Carrousel Avis Clients Photos\n\n  ============================================\n\n  Carrousel horizontal d'avis avec avatar et étoiles.\n\n  Défilement tactile sur mobile.\n\n{% endcomment %}\n\n \n\n<style>\n\n  .reviews-carousel {\n\n    padding: 24px 0;\n\n    margin: 20px 0;\n\n  }\n\n  .reviews-carousel__title {\n\n    font-size: 20px;\n\n    font-weight: 700;\n\n    text-align: center;\n\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n\n    color: #111827;\n\n  }\n\n  .reviews-carousel__track {\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    gap: 16px;\n\n    overflow-x: auto;\n\n    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n\n    padding: 4px 16px 16px;\n\n    scrollbar-width: none;\n\n  }\n\n  .reviews-carousel__track::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n\n  .review-card {\n\n    min-width: 280px;\n\n    max-width: 300px;\n\n    background: #fff;\n\n    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n\n    border-radius: 12px;\n\n    padding: 20px;\n\n    scroll-snap-align: start;\n\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n\n    transition: transform 0.2s;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }\n\n  .review-card__header {\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    align-items: center;\n\n    gap: 10px;\n\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__avatar {\n\n    width: 40px;\n\n    height: 40px;\n\n    border-radius: 50%;\n\n    background: #eff6ff;\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    align-items: center;\n\n    justify-content: center;\n\n    font-weight: 700;\n\n    color: #3b82f6;\n\n    font-size: 16px;\n\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__name {\n\n    font-weight: 600;\n\n    font-size: 14px;\n\n    color: #111827;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__badge {\n\n    font-size: 10px;\n\n    color: #10b981;\n\n    font-weight: 600;\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    align-items: center;\n\n    gap: 3px;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__stars {\n\n    color: #f59e0b;\n\n    font-size: 14px;\n\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__text {\n\n    font-size: 13px;\n\n    color: #4b5563;\n\n    line-height: 1.6;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__date {\n\n    font-size: 11px;\n\n    color: #9ca3af;\n\n    margin-top: 10px;\n\n  }\n\n</style>\n\n \n\n<div class=\"reviews-carousel\">\n\n  <h3 class=\"reviews-carousel__title\">Ce que nos clients disent</h3>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-carousel__track\">\n\n \n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">M</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Marie L.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">Produit de qualité exceptionnelle ! L'emballage était soigné et la livraison ultra rapide. Je recommande à 100%.</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 3 jours</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n \n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">T</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Thomas B.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">Deuxième commande ici et toujours aussi satisfait. Le service client est top, ils m'ont répondu en 1h.</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 1 semaine</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n \n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">S</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Sophie R.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">Très bon rapport qualité-prix. Le produit correspond parfaitement à la description. Petit bémol sur le délai, sinon parfait.</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 2 semaines</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n \n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">J</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Julien D.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">J'ai offert ce produit à ma femme, elle était ravie. La qualité est vraiment au rendez-vous. Bravo !</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 3 semaines</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n \n\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
